cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "alchemy-geom-tda: E(3)-equivariant geometric ML with TDA for Alchemy dataset"
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
authors:
  - alias: ThomasMoore25
repository-code: "https://github.com/ThomasMoore25/alchemy-geom-tda"
