  - alchemy-dataset
  - EGNN
  - SchNet
  - persistence-homology
license: MIT
version: "v32.38"
date-released: "2026-07-17"
abstract: >-
  Prediction of quantum-mechanical properties (mu, alpha, gap) of
  molecules from the Alchemy dataset (202,579 molecules) using
  E(3)-equivariant geometric deep learning (EGNN, SchNet) and
  topological data analysis (Vietoris-Rips persistence, Betti curves).
  Six model variants are implemented: FCNN baseline, SchNet, EGNN,
  EGNN+TDA (concat or FiLM), EGNN Vector (equivariant mu output),
  EGNN Vector+TDA.
